---

## ✨ Features

### 🚀 **FastAPI Backend**
- **Real-time Stock Quotes** - Live NSE stock prices via Yahoo Finance
- **Technical Indicators** - RSI, Moving Averages (SMA 20/50), Bollinger Bands
- **Stock Screeners** - Momentum and oversold stock detection algorithms
- **Portfolio Analytics** - P&L calculation, returns tracking, performance metrics
- **Interactive API Docs** - Auto-generated Swagger UI and ReDoc
- **RESTful Architecture** - Well-structured endpoints with proper error handling

### 📈 **Streamlit Frontend**
- **Multi-stock Comparison** - Track multiple stocks simultaneously
- **Interactive Charts** - Professional-grade Plotly visualizations
- **Portfolio Tracker** - Real-time P&L monitoring with metrics
- **Market Overview** - Key metrics and price movements at a glance
- **API Integration Demo** - Test endpoints directly from the UI
- **Responsive Design** - Works seamlessly on different screen sizes

### 📊 **Technical Analysis Capabilities**
- RSI (Relative Strength Index) with customizable periods
- Simple Moving Averages (SMA 20, SMA 50)
- Bollinger Bands with upper/lower channels
- Volume analysis and trend detection
- Momentum scoring algorithm
- Oversold/Overbought condition detection
- Custom technical signals generation

### 💼 **Portfolio Management**
- Real-time portfolio valuation
- Profit/Loss tracking (absolute and percentage)
- Position-wise performance metrics
- Portfolio diversification view
- Historical returns calculation
- Best/worst performer identification

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|-----------|------------|---------|
| **Backend Framework** | FastAPI | High-performance API development |
| **ASGI Server** | Uvicorn | Lightning-fast ASGI server |
| **Frontend Framework** | Streamlit | Rapid data application development |
| **Data Source** | Yahoo Finance (yfinance) | Real-time and historical market data |
| **Data Processing** | Pandas, NumPy | Data manipulation and analysis |
| **Visualization** | Plotly | Interactive financial charts |
| **HTTP Client** | Requests, Aiohttp | API communication |
| **Environment** | Python 3.8+ | Core programming language |

---

## 🚀 Quick Start Guide

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8 or higher
- pip package manager
- Virtual environment (recommended)
- Git (for cloning)

### Step-by-Step Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/full-stack-trading-application.git
cd full-stack-trading-application